{
  "stem": "16571.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 129.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because from there, they actually decided where to send you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because all the time, transports were arriving in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From there, they sent different people to different-- other different works all over Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as I said, I was sent to-- to Block 8.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't realize until years later that the block next to us was actually an experiment block.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would experimenting with people, killing them, injecting them with all different poisons and all the rest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This-- this is what I learned after reading books after.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But whilst I was there, I had no clue what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You see, they could-- they could kill people in one block, and then have a-- putting up a show for the Germans in another block.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were crazy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was just craziness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember one of my friends was telling me, there was a rumor that they were selecting people for the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "People started running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was nowhere to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They spread.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he stood his ground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And a German saw him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he said to me, for the next six or eight weeks he was fed with white bread and salamis.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He come up and he said, Juden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You was not afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You stood your ground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I watched you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that's how they were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And-- and probably round the corner he was-- he was put-- putting cyanide in-- in the gas chambers, and-- and going home to his family like he was going home from any other job.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And yet he saw this friend of mine, free-- he froze.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He didn't move from his ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he saw him, and he-- he said, he fed me and clothed me for four to six weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
